            <note xml:id="n187-3">Mai takes <!--  Add Syriac  --> as part. from <!--  Add Syriac  -->, “to shave,” and translates “prolixo capillo”; but Jo. Mal. p. 410, has ὁλοπόλιος, εὔμορφο… ἀγράμματος (Brooks).</note>
